messages.text: You said you were coming half an hour ago :P
Did you turn left at the lights like I said?
Yeah but it’s dark so it’s hard to see where I am. I just see rows of houses
I should have come to meet you :(
But you don’t know where you are…
You’re not making me feel better
I’ve been walking for a while but I suddenly feel like I know where I’m going
Did you see something you recognise?
No… It’s more I’m being drawn somewhere
Drawn to me? That’s cute … but a little cheesy :P
I think I must be going the wrong way though
Because there aren’t any streetlamps anymore
Ok stop. You’re definitely going in the wrong direction :P
I think I can see something in an upstairs window
But it’s weird … she’s really close to the window. Like she’s stood on the windowsill?
Oh god what if she jumps out?
It’s just a shadow in a window
No Nat. You can’t see what I see
You don’t even know what you see? You can see a shadow
I’m going to knock on the door at least
Who is going to open their door to a strange guy at night?
She didn’t even move from the window
Go back to the main road – I’ll come find you
But there’s someone in the house!
No they won’t get here in time
Look around! A street sign. A house number. Anything!
I think I see a street sign…
33 Warren Street? That can’t be right.
Because Warren Street is basically derelict
Full of abandoned houses – they’re gonna knock them all down soon
Think about it! All the houses are abandoned. There’s no electricity!
So why would anyone be there? How could there be a light on? How could you see a shadow? It’s impossible.
I think I saw her move
Adam tell me where you are.
I told you where I am!
I need to be with her
If you break down the door you’ll terrify some poor family
I don’t understand why you’re doing this!
If you can see the street sign you must be close
Thank god! I’m coming to find you
Don’t do anything until I get there
She’s still at the window but she won’t let me in
Of course she won’t! You’re being crazy!
But she wants me to be with her
Adam tell me what’s going on
She’s at the door right now?
Do NOT go inside that house
It might be dangerous! You don’t know what’s going on or who’s up there with her!
I just got to 33 Warren Street
and you’re right there’s a light on in the top room
This is so weird! It’s not possible!
I see the figure you saw…
But it’s not a woman’s shadow at the window
